# 🚀 DRIVER MATCHING SYSTEM - FINAL ARCHITECTURE

## 📌 System Overview

> Real-time driver-load matching system with Rule-based (Phase 1) and ML-based (Phase 2) support.
> Seamless switching via `ml_use: true/false` parameter.

